Summary:. I am a fan of Samsung TVs, but will not likely buy another Samsung BR DVD player. We contacted Samsung and were told to update our software. I tried and the most current software was already running. I have tried several different disks of the same movie from Netflix, and all have failed to play. Older BR DVD movies have not been a problem. The bottom line is that I would strongly recommend looking at another brand for BR DVD players.. 

