Pros:. Picture quality is great, good looks, Youtube support is neat.. 
Cons:. Has pausing issues with some new BluRay movies (UP, Star Trek, Harry Potter), while old ones work fine. Samsung put out firmware updates to correct issues with specific movies but introduces more problems as well.. 
Summary:. This player's hardware seems solid enough, but the firmware is simply not up to par. Consumers should not be beta-testers, all movies should work out of the box. BluRay technology has been out for a few years now so it should be better than this.. The BDP1600 came free with my Samsung TV (which is great), but I probably will not buy another Samsung player based on these experiences. Stick to their TVs.. 

